On Wednesday, Governor Perdue hosted a town hall meeting at Cape Fear Community College in Wilmington. Joining Governor Perdue were State Schools CEO Bill Harrison and Community College President Scott Ralls. A packed and lively crowd of 300 citizensasked questions and discussed education and workforce development issues with Governor Perdue, Harrison and Ralls.



